CVR nummer og bankkonto hvis vi skal have tilskud fra det offentlige eller andre organisationer

Formålsparagraf - helt nøgternt hvad hensigten er


Purpose:
The purpose the Didactia organization is to support self-learning. We aim to do this by building, hosting and maintaining a server,
which allows users to create, view and edit learning material on a wide range of subjects.

Motivation:
We believe that everyone learns best in their own fashion - that there is no single best way to teach a subject.
For this reason we do not believe in finding a concensus for each subject, but would rather invite people to provide new insights and
explanations, in order to support multiple learning styles.

By performing statistical analysis on the learning habits of large numbers of users, we hope to develop a system which will recommend
articles that will provide the optimal "learning path" for a specific user. By learning path, we refer to the sequence of articles
which will provide the prerequisite knowledge for the learning goals of the user.



Vedtægter (som minimum - se side 12-18):
1. Formål.
2. Hjemsted: https://github.com/didactia og http://www.didactia.org
3. Optagelsesbetingelser (eksklusion).
4. Kontingent.
5. Generalforsamling.
6. Bestyrelse.
7. Regnskab
8. Tegningsregler.
9. Vedtægtsændringer.
10. Opløsning.

Overvejelser vedr. bestyrelse
Bestyrelsens opgaver:
1. Udvikling af organisationen
2. Inddragelse af medlemmerne
3. Sikre overholdelse af vedtægterne
4. Kontakt til omverdenen
5. Fundraising og økonomistyring
6. Referater
7. Arkiv
8. Udvalg

Generalforsamlinger
Overvejelser ifb. med disse:
1. Tid og sted.
2. Dagsorden
3. Indkaldelse
4. Dirigent, referent og stemmetællere
5. Formandens/bestyrelsens beretning
6. Regnskab
7. Valg
